               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I was with one King over night, he borrowed a plough of me, and told me, to go to Draper's Hall for it, that I should find it on the left hand bench, and might take it, if he was not there.</p>
               <p>He called several witnesses to his character:</p>
